OL,3,CControversial allotment site 'doesn't
OL,4,Cneed planning permission', owners
OL,5,Cinsist
OL,7,FThe operators of a controversial
OL,8,Fallotment site near Bristol have
OL,9,Fdisputed demands that they must apply
OL,10,Ffor planning permission to stay open.
OL,12,FRoots Allotments told ITV News that
OL,13,FNorth Somerset Council has made a U-
OL,14,Fturn in asking for new approval for
OL,15,Fthem to operate in Abbots Leigh.
OL,17,FA deadline to comply by Thursday 15
OL,18,FAugust has been extended as talks
OL,19,Fbetween the parties continue.
