OL,5,Cinsist
OL,7,FRoots co-founder Will Gay said: "We'll
OL,8,Fobviously push back on some of the
OL,9,Fmore miscellaneous and strange items.
OL,11,F"The message we've been receiving from
OL,12,Fother councils around the country is
OL,13,Fthat 99% of the items here do not need
OL,14,Fplanning.
OL,16,F"We're liaising with our planning firm
OL,17,Fwho will go back to the council and
OL,18,Fdiscuss the items that they've
OL,19,Frequested us to apply for."
