OL,7,FHe added: "This business is perfect,
OL,8,Fyou get local people eating local
OL,9,Ffood, it's a great use of agricultural
OL,10,Fland and it's getting people outside
OL,11,Freconnecting with nature."
OL,13,FNorth Somerset Council initially
OL,14,Fgranted Roots a certificate of
OL,15,Flawfulness, but it is now demanding
OL,16,Fthe operators apply for planning
OL,17,Fpermission retrospectively.
