OL,7,FIt's thought items including water
OL,8,Ftroughs, matting to form an access
OL,9,Ftrack, and the siting of a metal
OL,10,Fcontainer need permission from the
OL,11,Flocal authority.
OL,13,FAround 3,000 people have signed a
OL,14,Fpetition opposing the site on land
OL,15,Fowned by the former tobacco family,
OL,16,FWills.
OL,18,FIt borders the busy A369 and critics
OL,19,Fsay the access is inadequate to cope
OL,20,Fwith the demands of traffic.
