OL,7,FSimon Talbot-Ponsonby, chairman of
OL,8,FAbbots Leigh Parish Council, claimed:
OL,9,F"All the way through, Roots have felt
OL,10,Fthat they know better. They feel that
OL,11,Fthey don't need planning and they just
OL,12,Fgo ahead regardless.
OL,14,F"They don't really care what local
OL,15,Fpeople say. I just can't help
OL,16,Fremembering what it was like, a
OL,17,Fbeautiful meadow and then I look at it
OL,18,Fnow and, to be quite honest, it's a
OL,19,Fmess."
