OL,7,FThe company estimates they'll spend
OL,8,F#400,000 on this site with money from
OL,9,Fventure capitalists.
OL,11,FThey say their hostile reception,
OL,12,Fwhich they claim has included a car
OL,13,Fdumped at their entrance and concrete
OL,14,Fpoured into padlocks, is unwarranted
OL,15,Fand won't deter them.
