OL,4,Cneed planning permission', owners
OL,5,Cinsist
OL,7,FFellow co-founder Christian Samuel
OL,8,Fsaid: "I think we have tried to hear
OL,9,Fpeople out, understand people's
OL,10,Fconcerns to the best of our ability
OL,11,Fand do as much work around that as
OL,12,Fpossible.
OL,14,F"There are thousands of people on
OL,15,Fwaiting lists. People have snapped up
OL,16,Fall of these wonderful plots to grow
OL,17,Ftheir own fruit and veg and we're
OL,18,Fdisappointed to see the council has U-
OL,19,Fturned once again."
