OL,7,FA statement from North Somerset
OL,8,FCouncil read: "We granted Roots a
OL,9,FCertificate of Lawfulness in November
OL,10,F2023 to use the land for allotments.
OL,12,F"Since then a number of additional
OL,13,Felements have been introduced at the
OL,14,Fsite which we believe do require
OL,15,Fplanning permission. We have notified
OL,16,Fthem of this requirement .... to apply
OL,17,Ffor planning permission
OL,18,Fretrospectively."
